item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - JADA Rare/Unreleased Songs
item.description:
I was wondering if anyone had these Unreleased tracks from the girl group JADA. They are commonly known for their song American Cowboy, released back in 2010, but they have far more songs than that one. Here are some of the songs I'm missing:

1. Do Your Thing
2. Model That
3. Shattered
4. Play A Playa
5. SuperModels
6. Follow My Procedure
7. Test Drive
8. Wrong Way
9. Nothing At All
10. Wishlist (Feat. Frankie J)
11. Make Up For Lost Time
12. Work It
14. Drives Me Wild
15. Blinded
16. Testify
17. Indigo
18. Anytime
19. Buck Wild
20. Inevitable
21. Anything
22. Everybody
23. Where Did All The Money Go?
24. Kiss And Tell (2 Min. Only)
25. U Gotta Go (2 Min. Only)

I have the songs U Gotta Go and Kiss And Tell, but I'm not sure it's the full songs, 'cause they kinda cut off at the end after playing for two minutes. So, if you have the full versions of those two tracks, that would be awesome.

Feel free to comment down below if you have the songs, or can point me in the direction I can go, to get the songs. Thank you
